{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1694-03_244","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Le Portrait du Sage","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mars 1694 [tome 3], p. 244-246.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Je vous envoye un Ouvrage qui dit beaucoup en peu de paroles, &amp; qui peint un caractere rare, quoy que le nombre des parties qui le composent ne soit pas grand. C’est le Portrait du Sage, qui trouvera toujours plus d’Admirateurs que de Sectateurs. Il est de M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" l’Abbé de Riupeirous, qui a fait paroistre son esprit par des Ouvrages de plus longue haleine, &amp; qui ont receu beaucoup d’applaudissemens.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"LE PORTRAIT","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"du Sage.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si dans le Monde il est un Sage","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qui sçache moderer ses vœux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seul il merite l’avantage","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De porter le titre d’heureux.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il vit content de sa fortune ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelque part que le Ciel l’ait mis,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jamais sa plainte n’importune","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ny les Princes, ny ses Amis.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il ignore le vil commerce","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les hommes font de leur cœur,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ne sçait point comment s’exerce","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’infame métier de flateur.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tous ses desseins sont legitimes,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et conformes à la raison ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est toujours juste, &amp; des crimes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ignore mesme le nom.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dégagé de toute contrainte,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le repos fait tout son plaisir,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et content, il voit tout sans crainte,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parce qu’il voit tout sans desir.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il joüit d’une paix profonde,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que nul revers ne peut troubler,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la cheute mesme du monde","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne pourroit le faire trembler.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}}}